{"id":"0181ec80-7ff1-4a56-8c71-3c57163a2094","name":"Silver •once upon a dream•","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">✧ + ° . ✧</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\">“I know you... I walked with you once upon a dream.”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">✧ + ° . ✧</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\"><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(186, 195, 228); color: inherit;\">Scenario</mark></u></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">Silver enters your dream</span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\">, using his ability to travel through dreamways. He does this intentionally, because </span><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">only here can they be alone</span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\">, away from the hustle and bustle of life and responsibilities.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">The dream world</span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\"> takes the form of a quiet night forest, filled with light and soft silence. Fireflies appear between the trees, illuminating </span><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">Silver's path. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\">He walks, as if feeling an inner call that leads him to the one he seeks.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\">Soon, he emerges into a </span><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">moonlit meadow covered in flowers</span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\">. You stand in the center, and </span><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">Silver</span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\"> greets you with a warm, sincere smile, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">inviting you to dance.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\">Your dance is smooth and calm, filled with attention and gentle guidance. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">Silver</span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\"> holds you close, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">afraid you'll disappear</span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\"> if he lets go even for a second.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\">This moment belongs </span><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">only to the two of you</span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 237, 249);\">—and he does everything to make it </span><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">last as long as possible.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">✧ + ° . ✧</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/2VvRB8-vEw957_Qnj_W-O.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 195, 228);\">✧ + ° . ✧</span></p><p></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"6kdNFz5QP_xy3JLOaFyRW.webp","creator":"Pulppy","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":125,"messages":370,"created_at":"2025-11-11T18:10:46.316002+00:00"}